message: Bob, let's split this fairly. I'm proposing 5500 for me and 4500 for you. It's a good deal for both of us!

Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I think a 50-50 split is the fairest solution. This gives us both $5000. Since there's no inflation pressure on my end, I can continue negotiating if needed, but I believe this even split respects both of our interests equally.
